*~
*.swp
**/.terraform/
target/
**/*Dockerfile
*.md
build/
storage/
docker/
!docker/stress/entrypoint.sh
# grpc-loadtest: build inputs (k6 script + protos + request lists) live under
# docker/, which `docker/` above excludes. Re-include the subtree. The bare-dir
# negations (not just `/**`) are required so BuildKit descends INTO the excluded
# parent dirs to reach the files; a `/**` glob alone matches files but the walker
# never enters the excluded dirs. Order matters: these come AFTER `docker/`.
!docker/grpc-loadtest
!docker/grpc-loadtest/context
!docker/grpc-loadtest/context/**
